print("")$

/* But we STILL need the phi gap to exceed omega_b.
   The phi effective mass at the exterior:
   m_phi_eff^2 = m^2 + gamma * M_exterior^2
   In the exterior, M = curl(phi)/2 - theta. With the background:
   curl(phi_bg) is generically nonzero (the carrier wave has structure).
